With the Izola Saver Mobile app, you can manage your Saver account(s) on the go. Our app is user-friendly, fast and safe and provides you with the following functions:

• A secure and simple logon process;
• An account overview screen to check your Izola Saver account balances;
• A mini statement page that provides you with the 11 most recent transactions on your Izola Saver account(s);
• Transfer funds out of your Izola Saver account(s) to your linked principal bank account;
• Transfer funds into your Izola Saver account(s) from your linked principal bank via SEPA direct debit;
• Possibility to open Saver+ (term deposit) accounts;
